[Warden_BD_Stances X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Stances"
LocLongDescription="Gain a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point by carrying out a turn-ending attack in the correct stance. Gain bonus sword aim and mobility in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font> and reduced enemy defense from cover and a critical hit bonus in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>. Receive an aim penalty of -<Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_AIM_PENALTY> when attacking using an incorrect stance / weapon combination."
LocHelpText="Gain a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point by carrying out a turn-ending attack in the correct stance. Gain bonus sword aim and mobility in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font> and reduced enemy defense from cover and a critical hit bonus in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>. Receive an aim penalty of -<Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_AIM_PENALTY> when attacking using an incorrect stance / weapon combination."
LocFlyOverText="Stances"

[Warden_BD_MeleeStance X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Melee Stance"
LocLongDescription="While in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim per proficiency rank."
LocHelpText="While in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim per proficiency rank."
LocFlyOverText="Melee Stance"

[Warden_BD_RangedStance X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Ranged Stance"
LocLongDescription="While in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance per proficiency rank."
LocHelpText="While in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance per proficiency rank."
LocFlyOverText="Ranged Stance"

[Warden_BD_WrongStancePenalties X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Stance Penalty"
LocLongDescription="While trying to use a <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged Weapon</font> in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee Stance</font>, receive a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_AIM_PENALTY/></font>% Aim penalty. While trying to use a <font color='#0058CA'>Melee Weapon</font> in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged Stance</font>, receive a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_AIM_PENALTY/></font>% Aim penalty."
LocHelpText="While trying to use a <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged Weapon</font> in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee Stance</font>, receive a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_AIM_PENALTY/></font>% Aim penalty. While trying to use a <font color='#0058CA'>Melee Weapon</font> in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>, receive a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_AIM_PENALTY/></font>% Aim penalty."
LocFlyOverText="Stance Penalty"

