[Warden_BD_ProficiencyPassives X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Proficiency Bonuses"
LocLongDescription="While in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim per proficiency rank. While in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance per proficiency rank. Gain additional charges of <font color='#8f3fbf'>Flow Mastery</font> at each proficiency rank."
LocHelpText="While in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim per proficiency rank. While in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>, gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance per proficiency rank. Gain additional charges of <font color='#8f3fbf'>Flow Mastery</font> at each proficiency rank."
LocFlyOverText="Proficiency Bonuses - Warden"

[Warden_BD_Rewind X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Blink"
LocLongDescription="Vanish and re-appear at your previous movement location. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:REWIND_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Vanish and re-appear at your previous movement location. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:REWIND_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Blink"

[Warden_BD_Mirror X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Reflective Barrier"
LocLongDescription="Create an elemental barrier on the Warden or an ally, which degrades the next <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_NUMBER_OF_ATTACKS/></font> incoming hits to grazes. Direct attacks on the barrier allow the Warden to return the damage psionically to the attacker. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Create an elemental barrier on the Warden or an ally, which degrades the next <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_NUMBER_OF_ATTACKS/></font> incoming hits to grazes. Direct attacks on the barrier barrier allow the Warden to return the damage psionically to the attacker. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MIRROR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Reflective Barrier"

