[Warden_BD_GrantImbueAmmoCharges X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Create Astral Bullet"
LocLongDescription="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced bullet at the start of each mission, and the ability to create additional bullets by using a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. Firing the bullets requires <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font> and a standard action point but does not require standard ammo. The bullets deal +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignore armor & shields and prevents units entering sustain, if killed. It cannot critically hit."
LocHelpText="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced bullet at the start of each mission, and the ability to create additional bullets by using a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. Firing the bullets requires <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font> and a standard action point but does not require standard ammo. The bullets deal +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:IMBUEAMMO_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignore armor & shields and prevents units entering sustain, if killed. It cannot critically hit."
LocFlyOverText="Create Astral Bullet"

[Warden_BD_GrantSoulBladeCharges X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Charge Soul-Blade"
LocLongDescription="Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced strike(s) and the ability to channel energy into the Warden's sword. Use a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point to create an additional charged attack which can be used on the next turn. The attack deals +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignores armor & shields and prevents units entering sustain, if killed. It cannot critically hit. The attack requires <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>."
LocHelpText=Grants <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_INITIAL_CHARGES/></font> psionically enhanced strike(s) and the ability to channel energy into the Warden's sword. Use a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point to create an additional charged attack which can be used on the next turn. The attack deals +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:SOULBLADE_DAMAGE_BONUS/></font> base damage, ignores armor & shields and prevents units entering sustain, if killed. The attack requires <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>."
LocFlyOverText="Soul-Blade"

