LocLongDescription="Each stance switch adds +<font color='#CA7200'>1</font> damage to all subsequent attacks made in the correct stance (Up to a maximum of +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEEFOCUS_MAXIMUM_BONUS/></font>)."
LocHelpText="Each stance switch adds +<font color='#CA7200'>1</font> damage to all subsequent attacks made in the correct stance (Up to a maximum of +<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEEFOCUS_MAXIMUM_BONUS/></font>)."
LocFlyOverText="Stance Unity"

[Warden_BD_Combatives X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Riposte"
LocLongDescription="Perform a counter-attack with your sword <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MAX_COUNTERATTACKS_ALLOWED/></font> times per turn against enemies that attempt to engage you with melee attacks. Passive."
LocHelpText="Perform a counter-attack with your sword <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MAX_COUNTERATTACKS_ALLOWED/></font> times per turn against enemies that attempt to engage you with melee attacks. Passive."
LocFlyOverText="Riposte"

[Warden_BD_Fissure X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Sundering Sigil"
LocLongDescription="Place a large psionic ward on the ground. Organic enemies will receive <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_INITIAL_AMOUNT/></font> stack of rupture and a further <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_AMOUNT/></font> stacks if they remain inside the ward at the end of the turn. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Place a large psionic ward on the ground. Organic enemies will receive <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_INITIAL_AMOUNT/></font> stack of rupture and a further <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_AMOUNT/></font> stacks if they remain inside the ward at the end of the turn. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FISSURE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Sundering Sigil"

[Warden_BD_Tide X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Tide"
LocLongDescription="Create a psionic shockwave that pushes back & damages non-flying enemies, ignoring cover & armour. Deals <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_DAMAGE/></font> damage in a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_AREA_OF_EFFECT/></font> tile radius around the warden and stuns all enemies for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_STUN_DURATION/></font> action points. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Knock down & damage non-flying enemies, ignoring cover & armour. Deals <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_DAMAGE/></font> damage in a <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_AREA_OF_EFFECT/></font> tile radius around the warden. Stuns for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_STUN_DURATION/></font> action points. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:TIDE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Tide"

[Warden_BD_Consume X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Consume"
LocLongDescription="Cleanse all mental and active damage-over-time effects from XCOM soldiers in the area of effect & provide them with immunity for 1 turn. Add <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_MULTIPLIER/></font> damage per turn remaining of each effect, to the Warden's next attack. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Cleanse all mental and active damage-over-time effects from XCOM soldiers in the area of effect & provide them with immunity for 1 turn. Add <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_MULTIPLIER/></font> damage per turn remaining of each effect, to the Warden's next attack. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CONSUME_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Consume"

[Warden_BD_ConsumeAdditionalDamage X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Consume Damage"
LocLongDescription="Adds additional damage to the warden's next attack"
LocHelpText="Adds additional damage to the warden's next attack"
LocFlyOverText="Consume Damage"

[Warden_BD_RagePassive X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Warden's Rage"
LocLongDescription="Standard shot can be activated from <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action points. Passive."
LocHelpText="Standard shot can be activated from <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action points. Passive."
LocFlyOverText="Warden's Rage"

[Warden_BD_FractureRanged X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Astral Barrage"
LocLongDescription="Gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FRACTURE_RANGED_BULLET_CHARGES/></font> Astral Bullets. Fire Astral Bullets at all enemies in Line of Sight until stacks (or targets) are exhausted. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FRACTURE_RANGED_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown. Uses standard action points. Resets bonuses gained from Stance Unity. Requires <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>. Also grants the Astral Bullet ability, if not present already."
LocHelpText="Gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FRACTURE_RANGED_BULLET_CHARGES/></font> Astral Bullets. Fire Astral Bullets at all enemies in Line of Sight until stacks (or targets) are exhausted. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FRACTURE_RANGED_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown. Resets bonuses gained from Stance Unity. Uses standard action points. Requires <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>. Also grants the Astral Bullet ability, if not present already."
LocFlyOverText="Fracture"

[Warden_BD_LastRites X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Last Rites"
LocHelpText="Gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_SOULBLADE_CHARGES/></font> soul-blade charges. Thrust your blade into an enemy and snap it off, leaving behind a fragment of your sword's energy. Teleport back to the turn start position. The fragment detonates in <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_DURATION/></font> turns, or on the next instance of psionic damage, dealing damage equal to that of all charges deposited. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown.  Resets bonuses gained from Stance Unity. Uses standard action points. Requires <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>. Grants the Soul-Blade ability, if not present already."
LocLongDescription="Gain <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_SOULBLADE_CHARGES/></font> soul-blade charges. Thrust your blade into an enemy and snap it off, leaving behind a fragment of your sword's energy. Teleport back to the turn start position. The fragment detonates in <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_DURATION/></font> turns, or on the next instance of psionic damage, dealing damage equal to that of all charges deposited. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown.  Resets bonuses gained from Stance Unity. Uses standard action points. Requires <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>. Grants the Soul-Blade ability, if not present already."
LocFlyOverText="Last Rites"

