LocHelpText="This unit has been marked by a Warden's Last Rites. The unit will receive damage from a devastating detonation in <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_DURATION/></font> turns, or on the next instance of psionic damage."
LocLongDescription="This unit has been marked by a Warden's Last Rites. The unit will receive damage from a devastating detonation in <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:LAST_RITES_DURATION/></font> turns, or on the next instance of psionic damage."
