LocFriendlyName="Warden's Call"
LocLongDescription="Replace a single <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point with three, which can be used sequentially on any abilities in the Warden's arsenal. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CHARGE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Replace a single <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point with three, which can be used sequentially on any abilities in the Warden's arsenal. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:CHARGE_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocFlyOverText="Warden's Call"

