LocLongDescription="Resets cooldowns on all abilities which can be activated with <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action points. Requires a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point, but does not consume it. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FLOWFOCUS_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown"
LocHelpText="Resets cooldowns on all abilities which can be activated with <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action points. Requires a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point, but does not consume it. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:FLOWFOCUS_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown"
LocFlyOverText="Flow Focus"

[Warden_BD_Retribution X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Sigil of Retribution"
LocLongDescription="Place a large psionic ward on the ground. All friendly, organic units standing in the area of effect will have their overwatch penalties removed. Units remaining inside the ward at the end of the turn will be granted a free overwatch shot. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RETRIBUTION_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Place a large psionic ward on the ground. All friendly, organic units standing in the area of effect will have their overwatch penalties removed. Units remaining inside the ward at the end of the turn will be granted a free overwatch shot. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RETRIBUTION_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
