LocLongDescription="Create a large obelisk at the target location, granting high cover lasting for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:PILLAR_NUMBER_OF_TURNS/></font> turns. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:PILLAR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Create a pillar at the target location. Grants high cover lasting for <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:PILLAR_NUMBER_OF_TURNS/></font> turns. Uses a <font color='#8f3fbf'>flow</font> action point. <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:PILLAR_COOLDOWN/></font>-turn cooldown."
