[WOTC_Prof_Warden_BD_AcademyAbility1 X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Warden: Warden's Concentration I"
LocLongDescription="Warden Proficiency abilities (+<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim while in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, plus <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>) will start at the second proficiency level (Normally granted at Sergeant), regardless of soldier rank."
LocHelpText="Warden: Warden's Concentration I"
LocPromotionPopupText="Warden Proficiency abilities (+<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_I_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_II_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:MELEESTANCE_III_MOBILITY_BONUS/></font> mobility and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_I_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_II_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:WARDENSSWORD_AIM_III_BONUS/></font> sword aim while in <font color='#0058CA'>Melee stance</font>, plus <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CDEF_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CDEF_BONUS/></font>% reduction in enemy defense from cover and <font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_I_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_II_CRIT_BONUS/></font>/<font color='#CA7200'><Ability:RANGEDSTANCE_III_CRIT_BONUS/></font>% critical hit chance in <font color='#CA7200'>Ranged stance</font>) will start at the second proficiency level (Normally granted at Sergeant), regardless of soldier rank."
LocFlyOverText="Prof GTS Unlocks"

